::Cygnar::
       "Actually I'm suggesting something quite different from both of 
those."  He looks at both of his fellow commanders intently.  "You are after 
all both my enemies.  You always will be, you must understand that.  I am 
merely suggesting that we put our differences aside to eliminate a common 
threat.  We will be allied until this battle is over.  Once Hydras is no 
more, we may discuss further agreements."

--part1_161.15e54986.2ae1aaad_boundary
